Class ModifyPartController

java.lang.Object
com.jpollock.c482.ModifyPartController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ModifyPartController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This class is used to control the Modify Part form so that the user is able to edit the Part they have selected.
